<br>
TIA... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=cumdar>Cumdar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/13/01 5:05:44 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: at lvl9, want to hit 12 quickly, where at?</span><hr size=1> You didn't mention what race or where you are currently so I'm guessing you don't mind traveling.  Here's where I have gone successfully.<br>
<br>
Steamfont - 5 skeletons spawn behind the cogs near the mino caves.  Great xp - decent cash - not often camped anymore.<br>
<br>
East/West Commons - at 9 stay in the east go near an in and fight whatever cons blue.  There guards near the in if you get over your head and usually PC's who will help if you /y.  At 10 get yourself a magic weapon and fight wisps in the West.  Good xp - decent cash - GREAT loot.  They drop lightstones and greater lightstones.  Save them and when you are full run/gate to NK and turn them into Myrsillia (or something) at the gypsie camp.  She will give you a book for each lightstone about 1pp ( I think) or for each Greater Light Stone (GLS) she will give you a concordance of research worth about 8pp ( I know.)  I have built up all my chars cash with the GLS's.  I will even buy some in West Commons for 5pp or less and turn them in for xp and sell the book for 8pp.  Gotta do it! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/upubar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>pubar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/14/01 10:37:09 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: at lvl9, want to hit 12 quickly, where at?</span><hr size=1> I am in the east commons currently, fighting the blue asps, pumas, rattlesnakes, and skeletons. This seems to be giving me good enough exp for my taste, I should hit 10 tonight. Thanks for the input...any one else?<br>
<br>
I am a high elf btw... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uorsmoxlorr.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Orsmo Xlorr</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/14/01 12:02:53 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> where at 10?</span><hr size=1> If you don't mind the trip.  Go to Qeynos Aquaducts and do the smuggler/thug rooms.  Smugglers room is a two spawn ( they both aggro) with a built in med point to avoid any wandering mobs.  Plus you get the dungeon bonus and VI recently added a 20% bonus to this zone because no one ever goes there.  But get a map and enter it from the false wall outside the city.  Also back by the smuggs in a begger in a room with 2 rats.  This is the only begger you should kill, unless you never want to go to the city of qeynos.  Easy XP and rarely camped.<br>
<br>
Orsmo Xlorr<br>
38 lvl Wizard<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/utehutibloodstorm.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tehuti Bloodstorm</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(7/22/01 5:47:35 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: where at 10?</span><hr size=1> Go to Lake Rathe, and do the Aviaks under the Arena entrance. Close to zone, and 4 solo pulls. Take you to 12 before you know it, low magic resist to boot. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=cumdar>Cumdar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(7/22/01 6:41:50 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: where at 10?</span><hr size=1> Would you like to make some money?<br>
<br>
Go to West Commons and root and shoot wisps till 14.  Collect Greater lightstones and lightstones.  GLS will get you 8-9pp and xp - LS will get you about 1-2pp and xp.  You turn them in at the gypsie camp in NK to Mrysilia.  I fund all my low level chars this way.  My wizard found out about it too late, but my shaman got 400pp this way.  I also would buy GLS's when I could find them for 5pp or less.  You get 3pp and xp for it and don't spend any mana that way.  Make sure you have a magical weapon though.  The little bastards can't be hit with regular weapons.  My wizzy used a Runed Totem Staff, but looking back I wish that I had practiced up my 1hb instead.  <br>
<br>
You get some books from her when you turn in the stones.  These are also the books you need to practice research.  But I think it is a pain in the butt.  Just sell them back to her and you get your cash.  Also when turning in GLS's make sure you have an open inventory slot since the book you get for them is a container. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=cumdar>Cumdar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(7/22/01 6:44:07 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: where at 10?</span><hr size=1> Geez - maybe I should have payed attention to the fact that I had already posted that.  Oops!<br>
<br>
Oh well, I gave more info this time anyway. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/unarach.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Narach</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(7/23/01 12:54:53 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Oasis</span><hr size=1> At level 4 i went to the oasis and stayed there, since you are already past the annoying first 8 levels, this would be a fairly decent place to go. Just get into a derv group, should be fairly easy.<br>
<br>
Then just camp them for a few levels, wont take long, just make sure you have a good group since you dont want to be running from your bind point (probably freeport) when/if you die.<br>
<br>
You can stay at the dervs up until level 16, when they dont give much, if any, exp. Killing dervs isnt that profitable. I got about 3/400pp from levels 9 to 16 by selling bronze stuff, and also the better gems to other players.<br>
<br>
Narach<br>
37th Wizard of The Red Wolf Clan<br>
Zeb server <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.showMessage?topicID=156.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.showMessage?topicID=155.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.emailToFriend?topicID=103.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.threadControl?topicID=103.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=103.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=103.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub23.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm1">General Discussion<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm3">Trade Forum<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm4">Rant Forum<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm8">Mob Dropped Spells<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm10">Class Balance & Class Bugs<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm22">Out of Mana<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm27">PVP Forum<option value="gra